  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/industry/\" rel=\"tag\">产业新闻</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/04/07/htc-q1-2014-earnings/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/c3c480dbe0c839c18bb29b2daae69d87/200012240/htc-one-m8-earnings-2014-04-07-01.jpg\" style=\"width: 620px; height: 346px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n在连续 28 个月销量不停<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/05/htc-q4-2013-earnings/\">下滑</a>后，HTC 终于在 3 月中止住<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/10/htc-eyes-off-the-ball-q1-forecast-2015/\">颓势</a>，将销量提升到了比一年前高 2.2% 的水平。但尽管如此，财报显示其上一季的营收仍只有 330 亿新台币，距离公司本已不算高的预期仍有一定的距离。除此之外，运营总亏损也比预想中来得更多。不过随着新旗舰 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/25/htc-announces-the-new-one/\">HTC One（M8）</a>的推出，HTC 对下一季的信心也水涨船高。能否实现久违的盈利，大家三个月后再见分晓。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/04/07/htc-q1-2014-earnings/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://investors.htc.com/phoenix.zhtml?c=148697&amp;p=irol-newsArticle&amp;ID=1916106&amp;highlight=\" target=\"_blank\">HTC</a></span><br />\n更多信息：<span class=\"more-coverage\"><a href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-04-07/htc-posts-second-loss-in-three-quarters-ahead-of-m8-smartphone.html\" target=\"_blank\">Bloomberg</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/04/07/htc-q1-2014-earnings/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20864304/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/04/07/htc-q1-2014-earnings/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
